DocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104gxr1665702610494.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gxr1665702610494.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/gxr1665702610494.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"gxr1665702610494\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Line\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">An Area is a Development Object that defines a vertical or horizontal line in the layout of a Form or Report component.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95969e1_d95970e1_d95971e1\">It is not possible to style a Line and a line cannot be\n      resized when the component is resized.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__section_f1m_54s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266596e54\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__image_wjc_x4s_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/frame_line.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">lin</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"euw1665702582150.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/euw1665702582150.html\" title=\"A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\">Form</a>. <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rvk1665702582227.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rvk1665702582227.html\" title=\"A Report is a Component that defines the content and layout of printed output of a Uniface application. It is not interactive and cannot be used to update the database.\">Report</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"gya1665702610097.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/gya1665702610097.html\" title=\"A Frame is a Development Object that graphically represents a Development Object in the layout of a Form or Report component.\">Frame</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">None</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"gxr1665702610494__table_d10643e1_d10644e1_d10645e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>/lin:<var class=\"keyword varname\">LineId</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__section_onn_y4s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266596e260\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95978e1_d95979e1_d95980e1\">Line specializes Frame in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__ul_crg_z4s_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38807e1_d38808e1_d38809e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95981e1_d95982e1_d95983e1\">It has no code containers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38810e1_d38811e1_d38812e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95984e1_d95985e1_d95986e1\">It can only have the component as a parent.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__section_bdl_z4s_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d266596e284\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95990e1_d95991e1_d95992e1\">Object properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__ul_if5_1ps_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38813e1_d38814e1_d38815e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38816e1_d38817e1_d38818e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38819e1_d38820e1_d38821e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__p_d95993e1_d95994e1_d95995e1\">Presentation properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__ul_pf5_1ps_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38822e1_d38823e1_d38824e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mpr1665702587008.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mpr1665702587008.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a horizontal axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Left (xpos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38825e1_d38826e1_d38827e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aon1665702587081.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aon1665702587081.html\" title=\"Position of an object frame on a vertical axis relative to its parent, excluding the border (if present); expressed as number of character cells.\">Top (ypos)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38828e1_d38829e1_d38830e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"swp1665702587155.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/swp1665702587155.html\" title=\"Width of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Width (xsize)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"gxr1665702610494__li_d38831e1_d38832e1_d38833e1\"><a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nai1665703058765.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nai1665703058765.html\" title=\"Height of the object frame in the layout of a Form or Report, expressed in character cells, excluding the border (if present).\">Height (ysize)</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613402\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3613402\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Line Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 03, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Line An Area is a Development Object that defines a vertical or horizontal line in the layout of a Form or Report component. It is not possible to style a Line and a line cannot be resized when the component is resized. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: lin Main Development Object? No Part of: Form . Report Contains: — Generalization: Frame Specializations: None Compilation Output: — URI format: cpt: ComponentName /lin: LineId Specialization Line specializes Frame in the following ways: It has no code containers. It can only have the component as a parent. Properties Object properties: Name Type Location Presentation properties: Left (xpos) Top (ypos) Width (xsize) Height (ysize) Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}